message: RT @jimwooley: Want to try out the new #Roslyn Compiler? head over to http://t.co/xOx55ysdVt to get the install package. #bldwin #Build2014
name: .NET Compiler Platform ("Roslyn")
caption: msdn.microsoft.com
description: The .NET Compiler Platform ("Roslyn") provides open-source C# and Visual Basic compilers with rich code analysis APIs. You can build code analysis tools with the same APIs that Microsoft is using to implement Visual Studio!
